{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ursid</strong> is a zen puzzle game inspired by the constellations and the beauty of their imaginary pictures. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the role of the little boy Aster, players will <strong>freely explore</strong> the star sky, <strong>connect</strong> the stars, <strong>find out</strong> the hidden images, and gradually reveal an emotional <strong>father-son story</strong> while counting down to the moment <strong>the Ursid Shower</strong> appears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/Unity_DURwYaeM0Y-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1732115096\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A total of 50+ handcrafted detailed levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Non-linear level solving progression. Players can freely choose the levels they want to solve, which follows the main story.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/connect-dots-ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1732115096\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Familiar connecting dots mechanics, which is refreshed by adding the challenge of hint numbers. Sometimes to find out a constellation needs a little bit of imagination!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cozy and meditative atmosphere with a heartwarming story about father-son relationship.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/extras/Unity_kvHzTp3DZn-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1732115096\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925290/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732115096","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2